### Health check
GET {{base_url}}/health
Accept: application/json


### Readiness check (includes DB ping)
GET {{base_url}}/readiness
Accept: application/json


### --- Bank Transactions ---

### List bank transactions (full page)
GET {{base_url}}/bank-txns/?budget={{ynab_budget_id}}&account={{ynab_account_id}}&status=pending&page=1&limit=20
Accept: text/html


### List bank transaction rows only (HTMX infinite scroll)
GET {{base_url}}/bank-txns/rows?budget={{ynab_budget_id}}&account={{ynab_account_id}}&status=pending&page=1&limit=20
Accept: text/html


### Get transaction detail panel
GET {{base_url}}/bank-txns/<id>/detail
Accept: text/html


### Skip a single transaction
POST {{base_url}}/bank-txns/<id>/skip?accId={{ynab_account_id}}&status=pending
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded


### Save inline transaction (sets payee + category, records pattern)
POST {{base_url}}/bank-txns/<id>/save-inline?status=pending
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

budget={{ynab_budget_id}}&account={{ynab_account_id}}&payee=<payee_id>&category=<category_id>&memo=Coffee&amount=-1500&txnDate=2026-06-27


### Bulk skip transactions
POST {{base_url}}/bank-txns/bulk-skip
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

txn_ids[]=<id1>&txn_ids[]=<id2>&account_id={{ynab_account_id}}


### --- Suggestions (JSON) ---

### Payee suggestions
GET {{base_url}}/bank-txns/api/payee-suggestions?budget_id={{ynab_budget_id}}&description=Amazon
Accept: application/json


### Category suggestions
GET {{base_url}}/bank-txns/api/category-suggestions?budget_id={{ynab_budget_id}}&description=Amazon&payee_id=<payee_id>
Accept: application/json


### --- Import Flow ---

### Preview bank transactions from CSV (shows diff before committing)
POST {{base_url}}/preview-bank-txns
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="budget"

{{ynab_budget_id}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="account"

{{ynab_account_id}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="txn-file"; filename="revolut.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< /Users/lex/Downloads/revolut.csv
--WebAppBoundary--


### Confirm import (uses file_uuid from preview response)
POST {{base_url}}/confirm-bank-txns
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

file_uuid=<file_uuid>&budget={{ynab_budget_id}}&account={{ynab_account_id}}


### Cancel preview (deletes temp file)
POST {{base_url}}/cancel-preview
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

file_uuid=<file_uuid>


### Upload bank transactions directly (no preview step)
POST {{base_url}}/upload-bank-txns
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="budget"

{{ynab_budget_id}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="account"

{{ynab_account_id}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="txn-file"; filename="revolut.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< /Users/lex/Downloads/revolut.csv
--WebAppBoundary--


### --- YNAB Sync ---

### Push transaction to YNAB
POST {{base_url}}/ynab-add-txn
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

budget={{ynab_budget_id}}&account={{ynab_account_id}}&payee=<payee_id>&category=<category_id>&memo=Coffee&amount=-1500&txnDate=2026-06-27


### Sync YNAB budgets
POST {{base_url}}/ynab-budgets-sync
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded


### Sync YNAB accounts
POST {{base_url}}/ynab-accs-sync
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded


### Sync YNAB categories
POST {{base_url}}/ynab-categories-sync
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded


### Sync YNAB payees
POST {{base_url}}/ynab-payee-sync
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded


### View sync history
GET {{base_url}}/sync-history
Accept: text/html
